rComments: He is one of a kind, the only professor I've had in 3 years to relate with the students. Wish I could take the course again for fun I loved it so much and he's super good looking too!

He is by far the BEST teacher I ever HAD! He is willing to help anyone and everyone for anything! He's incredibly easy to talk to and always in good spirits! I would go out of my way to take another class he teaches. He's also has amazing personal experience on his topics. LOVE HIM!!

A really fantastic prof, makes a point of talking to each and every student about their papers and provides really good feedback. The course was definitely my easiest, but he really wants to help you lay good foundations for your future university work. Great prof!
